uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May.-Credit-GIBSON.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May.-Credit-GIBSON-400x267.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May.-Credit-GIBSON-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May.-Credit-GIBSON-696x464.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May.-Credit-GIBSON-1392x928.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May.-Credit-GIBSON-1068x712.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Queen">皇后</a>的<a href="/artists/Brian-May">布莱恩·梅（Brian May）</a>与吉布森（Gibson）合作推出了全新的限量版12弦原吉他。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/brian-may-queen-in-3d-2083058">“女王日”：布莱恩·梅（Brian May）反思他的摇滚乐旅程</a></strong></li></ul><p>Gibson Custom的Brian May SJ-200 12弦原声吉他是与标志性吉他手和摇滚偶像密切合作的。从5月开始的大量设计输入创建，只有100个吉他模型将在通过<a href="https://cflu578ab.cc.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001roPmO4Ed2ID9TW3ZoHEbTLoiwLGxsbXsLPUl8soEAP30FPzsPfcL4nN45yk1nlw9lIt-9DWF81HlEnWGNuLUbcHrPixo9CcZVxIAA09sQwXf1Gfp0UgYdYW6ltjhTNqeQ8DW3i5CwlJSil0dCD0i0g==&amp;c=eppKuxNIidx4m8eFLfyJrRqHeIwSvKP8p1r7Ac4h5BIm9XZk2qCUpQ==&amp;ch=N6ExGskr1yI0ySY5_cvlEF4a6m5NhRJxDD1blitYLRII9jtdMCTiEA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gibson.com</a> ，Gibson Garage Nashville和London的有限运行中在全球范围内提供，并获得了授权的Gibson经销商。</p><p>在谈到吉他和新闻稿中的合作时，梅分享道：“这把吉他的想法是在我需要12弦的巡回演出时出现的，而我习惯的那个吉他的想法并没有在舞台上表演。吉布森（Gibson）的家伙非常友善地说：“我们将为您提供一些特别的东西，您可以在旅行中使用。”我要求的一件事是，将八度放置在通常的方法上，因为我喜欢上升并在演奏时听到前调。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="布莱恩·梅（Brian May）介绍了他的吉布森（Gibson）SJ-200 12-string |复古阳光" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ujw-bPWg8XY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我喜欢听到高八度的声音，然后我可以在上面演奏音乐。如果您看一下这把吉他，它的美丽以及声音的美丽，并看一下吉他中的科学，看看这把吉他的技术和工艺已经有多少。吉布森（Gibson）能够以象征意义的方式将宇宙放在上面，而《星球》（Planet Mercury）就在这里，这对我的一个总是与我同在的朋友有点点头。”</p><p>吉布森首席执行官Cesar Gueikian还补充说：“作为开拓性的声音先驱，潮流引领者，以及有史以来最有影响力的音乐家之一，与布莱恩·梅爵士（Sir Brian May）合作是绝对的特权。布莱恩对音乐和文化的影响是首屈一指的，这是我个人音乐之旅的变革影响。我们非常荣幸布莱恩（Brian）用这款SJ-200 12弦吉他信任吉布森（Gibson），我们很高兴最终将其带给世界各地的音乐爱好者。谢谢你，布莱恩。”</p><p>吉他具有优质的木材，包括AAA玫瑰木的背部和侧面，AAA Sitka云杉顶，带有老式的阳光饰面和2件式AAAAA枫木脖子，带有圆形的轮廓，胡桃木丝绸和带有Agoya Shell 8点的Rosewood Fretboard星际镶嵌。 </p><figure id="attachment_3839491" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3839491" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3839491" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON.jpg" alt="Brian May X吉布森爵士。学分：吉布森" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3839491" class="wp-caption-text"> Brian May X吉布森爵士。学分：吉布森</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3839492" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3839492" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3839492" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON-1.jpg" alt="Brian May X吉布森爵士。学分：吉布森" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sir-Brian-May-x-Gibson-guitar.-Credit-GIBSON-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3839492" class="wp-caption-text"> Brian May X吉布森爵士。学分：吉布森</figcaption></figure><p>床头库还设有令人惊叹的8点Agoya Shell明星镶嵌物，以及一个以行星为主题的Pickguard，由May设计为庆祝他对科学的热爱。</p><p>谈到吉他的设计和对他已故的前队友和女王主持人<a href="/artists/Freddie-Mercury">弗雷迪·水星（Freddie Mercury</a> ）的点头，在接受吉布森采访时，梅分享道：“弗雷迪总是和我在一起我们的婚姻。这是一件大事，仍然是。即使我们没有Freddie，我们仍然随身携带女王，但是我现在吉他上有一只汞，这让我很高兴。</p><p>他继续说：“我希望我父亲在身边看到它，因为这是他梦dream以求的事情。” </p><figure id="attachment_3839493" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3839493" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3839493" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-May-and-his-Red-Special-guitar.jpg" alt="皇后的布莱恩·梅（Brian May）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-May-and-his-Red-Special-guitar.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-May-and-his-Red-Special-guitar-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-May-and-his-Red-Special-guitar-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-May-and-his-Red-Special-guitar-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-May-and-his-Red-Special-guitar-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-May-and-his-Red-Special-guitar-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3839493" class="wp-caption-text">皇后的布莱恩·梅（Brian May） </figcaption></figure><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="布莱恩·梅（Brian May）：“ Foo Fighters很危险”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kc-o_3zjorA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>梅和他的父亲在60年代后期十几岁的时候就建造了音乐家的传奇和标志性红色特殊吉他。五月意识到他无法从Fender，Gibson或Höfner等知名人士中买不起吉他的吉他，这是与父亲一起建造自己的吉他的灵感。两人于1963年8月开始使用吉他，并于1964年10月一年后完成。</p><p>在其他新闻中，梅最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-may">对他的担心，他担心去年中风后永远不会再弹吉他</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/queens-brian-may-launches-new-12-string-acoustic-guitar-with-gibson-i-wish-my-dad-was-here-to-see-this-3839464">皇后的布莱恩·梅（Brian May）与吉布森（Gibson）一起推出了新的12弦原声吉他：“我希望我父亲在这里看到这一点”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
