@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/biggie-prince-smith@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/biggie-prince-smith@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/biggie-prince-smith@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/biggie-prince-smith@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/biggie-prince-smith@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-smith">Will Smith</a> has recalled speaking to both <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">Prince</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/biggie-smalls">Biggie Smalls</a> just hours before they died.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/best-prince-songs-9053"><b>The 20 best Prince songs of all time by the NME office</b></a></strong></li></ul><p> The actor and rapper opened up about his connection to the two of them during a new interview on the Broken Record podcast, and said that he feels a strange connection with the two music icons because of the last discussions he had with them.</p><p> Biggie Smalls, also known as the Notorious BIG, was murdered aged 24 during a drive-by shooting in Los Angeles back in March 1997. <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/prince-96-1205144">Prince died in 2016</a> from an accidental overdose of the painkiller fentanyl. He was aged 57.</p><p> “I don&#39;t even want to say this out loud &#39;cause it&#39;s like a terrible jinx,” Smith said during the interview. “I met Biggie four hours before he got killed, and I talked to Prince eight hours before he died.”</p><p> The latter, he explained, saw Prince call him up and pitch a business venture between the two of them and <a href="/artists/jay-z">Jay-Z</a> . This, he recalled, was an entertainment company that both he and the &#39;Empire State Of Mind&#39; rapper were interested in pursuing.</p><p> “He had talked to Jay and he wanted to do it. We talked that night, and in the morning, he was gone,” Smith said. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="威尔·史密斯|破纪录播客（完整剧集）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HqMbCPQjnBY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> As for his final communications with Biggie Smalls, the <em>I, Robot</em> actor shared how the untimely death of the rap icon had a huge effect on him. “It was stupid and just centred on hip-hop for rapping… That one hurt me. It scared me, too,” he said.</p><p> Recalling the strange coincidence between the discussions with The Notorious BIG and Prince, Smith went on to joke that it could be bad luck to talk to him. “I don&#39;t know what that says about me. Don&#39;t call me!”</p><p> In other news, Will Smith has been <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/will-smith-will-release-first-album-in-almost-20-years-under-new-record-deal-with-slang-3777945">focusing on his return to music in recent times</a> , making his comeback last year with the single <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/will-smith-says-work-of-art-made-him-find-his-voice-dance-in-your-darkest-moments-album-3779400">&#39;Work Of Art&#39; featuring his son Jaden and Russ</a> , followed by <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-will-smiths-assertive-new-single-tantrum-with-joyner-lucas-3822127">&#39;Tantrum&#39; with Joyner Lucas</a> .</p><p> Both songs are expected to be part of an upcoming album &#39;Dance In Your Darkest Days&#39;. The album has yet to receive a release date and will be his first since 2005&#39;s &#39;Lost And Found&#39;.</p><p> Since then, he has also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/will-smith-taps-big-sean-for-upcoming-single-beautiful-scars-shares-the-matrix-inspired-trailer-3832108">enlisted Big Sean for a new single titled &#39;Beautiful Scars&#39;</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/will-smith-spoke-to-prince-and-biggie-smalls-just-hours-before-they-died-3839443">Will Smith says he spoke to both Prince and Biggie Smalls just hours before they died</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
